Package edu.umn.biomedicus.uima.rtfrewriting

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotationInsertingWriter
    Inserts placeholders for annotations into RTF documents.
    RegionTagger
    Inserts tags before and after a region in an rtf document.
    RegionTaggerBuilder
    Builds a RegionTagger object.
    RtfRewriterCursor
    Class for rewriting an rtf document.
    SpecialTableMarker
    Inserts a marker at the end of a special table (color table, stylesheet, etc) in rtf, along with the number of entries that table contains.
    SymbolIndexedDocument
    A rtf document for modification, contains indices to all the symbols, which are entire control words or characters in the rtf document.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    SpecialTableNotFoundException
    Thrown when a special table is not found.
